"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"Under the condition that cryptocurrency becomes a legal currency, the Central Bank of Brazil would be allowed to issue a digital real central bank digital currency (CBDC). This would put Brazil among [nine other countries](https://cointelegraph.com/news/eastern-caribbean-cbdc-expands-to-another-two-territories) or jurisdictions that currently issue CBDC to its residents.\\n\\nBrazil currently produces just under [half](https://www.trade.gov/country-commercial-guides/brazil-energy) of its electricity from renewable sources, according to the International Trade Administration. The cost per kilowatt hour is about [$0.12](https://www.globalpetrolprices.com/Brazil/electricity_prices/), putting it roughly in the middle of the global pack in that regard.\",\"timestamp\":1639139655,\"title\":\"will not be shaken by the pandemic and economic\"},\"digest\":\"hvrf0vY58UqDFAhjG2SKhLfPQucjJC4tp2OkY8IGyf4\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x89cF485c4A8eB4A2E80aC39c2c611A83b2F23965\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"SveY0WtW456_RS1O3PsotNJsWFx4ajQyE13hLRIcbcs\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"xtEDDcFzzRKUHqFJGSsNozaHo5iTFbcPUjV0j_oW8cY\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"XjHBDJc_T7edkkxzuKvDi8bhVqWalzMkWR_fi8_ltmKdu4HP7dXlmpFsT_tnjcEhSrJr9NRwewFM5-yq4orvGA\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x634d9a126e408ba8b8ca321b1e9b70eff752c893e72037c47ecd509c9e7a69590f2b5f160a824d0fefc6b5cdada56408246188200b0ac48d02194cafb2560e751b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"SveY0WtW456_RS1O3PsotNJsWFx4ajQyE13hLRIcbcs\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"xtEDDcFzzRKUHqFJGSsNozaHo5iTFbcPUjV0j_oW8cY\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"hvrf0vY58UqDFAhjG2SKhLfPQucjJC4tp2OkY8IGyf4\"}"